This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, Primary Objectives:, To assess the effects of pharmaceutical, physical and surgical therapies in people with localised excessive sweating., Furthermore it will be investigated if the effect of the treatment varies according to the area treated (axillar, palmar, plantar and other)., Secondary Objectives:, To determine if certain variables influence the main effect of treatment. These variables include the duration and severity of symptoms and adverse effects